name: Waagaga!
body:
### Fresh Food Fast!
Waagaga is the newest concept in healthy, fresh eating. Faster, cheaper and simpler than fast food, but more convenient than the grocery store.

### Looking for Franchisees!
Get in on the ground floor. We're currently looking for master franchisees for Western and Atlantic Canada. Contact us today.
